<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>Guru Application Approved</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
      .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
      .header { background-color: #14a800; padding: 24px; text-align: center; }
      .header h1 { color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 24px; }
      .body { padding: 32px; }
      .body p { color: #444444; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; }
      .info-box { background-color: #f0faf0; border-left: 4px solid #14a800; border-radius: 4px; padding: 16px; margin: 24px 0; }
      .info-box p { margin: 4px 0; color: #276749; font-size: 14px; }
      .footer { background-color: #f4f4f4; text-align: center; padding: 16px; color: #aaaaaa; font-size: 12px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>GeniusBid</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="body">
        <p>Hi <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>

        <p>
          Congratulations! We're excited to let you know that your application
          to become a <strong>Guru</strong> on GeniusBid has been
          <strong>approved</strong>.
        </p>

        <p>
          Your profile is now active, and you can start receiving booking
          requests from clients looking for your expertise.
        </p>

        <div class="info-box">
          <p><strong>Specialty:</strong> <%= specialty %></p>
          <p><strong>Session Rate:</strong> $<%= sessionRate %>/hour</p>
          <p><strong>Status:</strong> Approved ✅</p>
        </div>

        <p>
          We encourage you to keep your profile updated, respond promptly to
          booking requests, and provide exceptional service to build your
          reputation within the GeniusBid community.
        </p>

        <p>
          Thank you for joining GeniusBid. We look forward to seeing you help
          clients achieve their goals.
        </p>

        <p>
          Best regards,<br />
          <strong>The GeniusBid Team</strong>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        &copy; <%= year %> GeniusBid. All rights reserved.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>